OL,3,CMan wrongly tasered by police says
OL,4,Cforce isn't taking accountability
OL,6,FA man who was wrongly identified and
OL,7,Ftasered by the Metropolitan Police
OL,8,Fsays the force isn't taking
OL,9,Faccountability for their actions.
OL,11,FAbdul-Lateef Ajibike was 17 when
OL,12,Ffirearms officers detained him whilst
OL,13,Fsearching for an armed suspect at a
OL,14,Fchip shop in Newham in 2023.
OL,16,FHe was tasered twice and pushed up
OL,17,Fagainst the wall for more than two
OL,18,Fminutes before officers realised their
OL,19,Fmistake.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
