FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783694874
OL,3,CMan wrongly tasered by police says
OL,4,Cforce isn't taking accountability
OL,6,FThe incident left him bleeding,
OL,7,Fbruised and unable to leave his house.
OL,9,FNow, aged 20, he's still unsure why
OL,10,Fpolice targeted him.
OL,12,FAbdul-Lateef said: "I've cried more in
OL,13,Fthis three years than I have the
OL,14,Fprevious 17 years of my life
OL,15,Fbeforehand.
OL,17,F"If I've been honest, it's like only
OL,18,Frecently when I realised that I'm not
OL,19,Fokay."
OL,26,@tD@TOUyD@AOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
