OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783694874
OL,3,CMan wrongly tasered by police says
OL,4,Cforce isn't taking accountability
OL,6,FFootage shows how officers violently
OL,7,Fapprehended him despite having
OL,8,Finformation indicating that the
OL,9,Fsuspect had already left the area.
OL,11,FAbdul-Lateef was pushed up against the
OL,12,Fwall for just over two minutes.
OL,14,FDuring that time, he was put in
OL,15,Fhandcuffs with a gun pointed at his
OL,16,Fhead.
OL,18,FThe case also reflects wider concerns
OL,19,Fabout Black children being
OL,20,Fdisproportionately targeted in use-of-
OL,21,Fforce incidents.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
