FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783694874
OL,3,CMan wrongly tasered by police says
OL,4,Cforce isn't taking accountability
OL,6,FAbdul-Lateef said:
OL,8,F"In this case, I'm guessing they just
OL,9,Fheard 'Black guy,' and 'Black guy in
OL,10,Ffish and chip shop,' which was me."
OL,12,FAbdul-Lateef's lawyers allege that
OL,13,Fofficers discriminated against him
OL,14,Fbecause of his race.
OL,16,FWith discrimination allegations, IOPC
OL,17,Fguidelines require officers to reflect
OL,18,Fon whether they could have done
OL,19,Fanything differently to change the
OL,20,Fcomplainant's experience of
OL,21,Fdiscrimination.
OL,26,@rD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
