OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783694874
OL,3,CMan wrongly tasered by police says
OL,4,Cforce isn't taking accountability
OL,6,FIn this case, every officer responded
OL,7,Fwith a variation of: "I don't feel
OL,8,Fanything could have been done
OL,9,Fdifferently."
OL,11,FThe allegation wasn't upheld but it
OL,12,Fdid conclude that some officers could
OL,13,Fhave been more open in their
OL,14,Freflections, describing it as an
OL,15,F"opportunity" for "learning or
OL,16,Fimprovement in practice".
OL,18,FAfter the incident, Abdul-Lateef was
OL,19,Fhousebound for two weeks and missed
OL,20,Ftwo months of school.
OL,26,@oD@VOUqD@MO]wD@AOUwD@MO]wD@SOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
