CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783694874
OL,3,CMan wrongly tasered by police says
OL,4,Cforce isn't taking accountability
OL,6,FHe fell behind with his coursework and
OL,7,Fexams, which impacted his grades and
OL,8,Fcomplicated his route to university.
OL,10,FThe civil case has been settled but
OL,11,FAbdul-Lateef says he still has
OL,12,Fflashbacks and nightmares.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/6
